HEADWORD: Lucent
<hw>Lu"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>lucens</ets>,
p. pr. of <ets>lucere</ets> to shine, fr. <ets>lux</ets>,
<ets>lucis</ets>, light.]</ety> <def>Shining; bright; resplendent.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧ The sun's <xex>lucent</xex> orb.⟦rdquo⟧
